OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be partly cloudy with scattered
OL,7,Fshowers, heavy at first. Then the rest
OL,8,Fof the night will see variable amounts
OL,9,Fof cloud and some showery rain.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,12,Fand a few showers, these becoming
OL,13,Flighter and fewer in the afternoon.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,16,FCloudy on Thursday with rain in the
OL,17,Fmorning, and again later in the day.
OL,18,FMainly dry, bright and warm on Friday.
OL,19,FChance of early rain on Saturday,
OL,20,Fotherwise dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
